TITLE: Defining a Persistent Pinia Store
DESCRIPTION: Example of defining a Pinia store with count state and associated methods. The store is configured for persistence with the persist: true option.
SOURCE: https://github.com/feige996/unibest/blob/main/docs/base/9-state.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: ts
